00:32:57.047 --> 00:32:59.179
Then, I'll do all the talking.

458
00:33:01.894 --> 00:33:04.005
I got a cell phone.

459
00:33:04.929 --> 00:33:07.289
But I can't call anyone.

460
00:33:07.289 --> 00:33:11.269
Mom told me not to
call anyone besides her.

461
00:33:12.564 --> 00:33:16.781
Also, I don't know
anyone's phone number.

462
00:33:16.781 --> 00:33:18.890
I don't know my own
phone number, either.

463
00:33:21.369 --> 00:33:23.855
We'll be leaving soon.

464
00:33:25.965 --> 00:33:30.330
When I'm all grown up,
I'll come see you by myself.

465
00:33:30.851 --> 00:33:33.702
I'll remember how to get here.

466
00:33:39.534 --> 00:33:41.727
I have to go now, Granny.

467
00:33:42.612 --> 00:33:44.092
Bye.

468
00:34:01.164 --> 00:34:02.775
Um, yes.

469
00:34:03.498 --> 00:34:04.498
Yes.

470
00:34:05.059 --> 00:34:06.467
Of course.

471
00:34:13.027 --> 00:34:14.777
Yes, then, just a second.

472
00:34:14.777 --> 00:34:17.110
I'll write it down.

473
00:34:17.110 --> 00:34:18.570
Yes, yes, yes.

474
00:34:18.570 --> 00:34:20.045
Oh no!

475
00:34:21.003 --> 00:34:23.347
Goodness!

476
00:34:25.820 --> 00:34:28.666
Oh, no, no, no.
I'm sorry.

477
00:34:28.666 --> 00:34:31.737
I'll call you right back. I'm sorry.

478
00:34:33.014 --> 00:34:35.572
Damn it!

479
00:34:39.945 --> 00:34:43.063
Damn it, what do I do?

480
00:34:46.474 --> 00:34:48.275
Oh, I'm sorry.

481
00:34:48.275 --> 00:34:50.398
My mind was all over the place.

482
00:34:51.282 --> 00:34:53.925
You're not hurt, are you?

483
00:34:55.168 --> 00:34:58.764
Oh, um, what was that about?
I'm very busy, you know.

484
00:34:58.764 --> 00:35:00.476
- Ugh.
- I'm sorry.

485
00:35:00.476 --> 00:35:03.061
I thought I left my car in park.

486
00:35:03.061 --> 00:35:04.108
I'm sorry.

487
00:35:04.108 --> 00:35:06.494
All right, so hurry
and call your insurance company.

488
00:35:06.494 --> 00:35:07.514
Yes, sure.

489
00:35:07.514 --> 00:35:09.476
I'll call them right now.

490
00:35:09.476 --> 00:35:11.476
I'm sorry.

491
00:35:16.565 --> 00:35:18.099
Hello?

492
00:35:18.099 --> 00:35:19.592
Excuse me.

493
00:35:20.119 --> 00:35:21.927
I want to report an accident.

494
00:35:21.927 --> 00:35:24.177
This guy was the one
who crashed into you.

495
00:35:24.827 --> 00:35:26.215
What?

496
00:35:26.215 --> 00:35:29.989
This guy's car backed
into yours, miss.

497
00:35:29.989 --> 00:35:31.887
You didn't crash into him.

498
00:35:31.887 --> 00:35:35.630
Ugh, I'm so busy as it is! Damn it!

499
00:35:35.630 --> 00:35:37.702
I saw everything.

500
00:35:40.831 --> 00:35:43.309
I'm sorry, I'll call you back.

501
00:35:44.018 --> 00:35:46.398
I'll check my dash cam,
if you don't mind.

502
00:35:51.074 --> 00:35:52.324
Damn it!

503
00:35:53.099 --> 00:35:54.929
That thug!

